          <h2 id="cont">Welcome to my website</h2>
          <p>I am Yogesh Balaji, math lover, coding freak and a tech enthusiast. I am currently in the fourth year of my B.tech program in Electrical Engineering at IIT Madras. I am working with Prof. A.N.Rajagopalan on motion blur using Deep Learning. From my first year, I was working on Computer Vision, but recently I started moving more into applications of Machine learning in vision. My research interest span a wide range of areas comprising Computer Vision, Machine Learning, Image Processing, Computational Imaging and Natural language Processing. I also enjoy working on analysis of communication protocols and scheduling algorithms. </p>
          
           
          
